---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="page">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      I'm a Linux systems consultant based in Oslo. I work with Kubernetes, GitOps, and automation—mostly with
      companies that have compliance requirements and can't afford surprises.
    </p>

    <div class="section" aria-labelledby="about-skills">
      <h2 id="about-skills">Skills</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Linux server administration (RHEL)</li>
        <li>Kubernetes (K3s/MKS) and GitOps with ArgoCD</li>
        <li>Secrets management (Vault, OpenBao)</li>
        <li>Automation with Ansible</li>
        <li>Experience working in PCI-DSS environments</li>
        <li>Splunk and Elastic Stack for log analysis</li>
        <li>AI-assisted coding with Claude Code and OpenCode</li>
        <li>Experimenting with agentic workflows and MCP servers</li>
        <li>Fine-tuning models for infrastructure and ops tasks</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section" aria-labelledby="about-linkedin">
      <p>
        The full career stuff is on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/eirik-breen" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
